README File for *tools* Directory
----------------------------------

The tools directory is a new feature starting in
VCCTL Version 3.0

Contents 
--------

In Version 3.0, the directory structure is

	./tools
		.
		.... cement-analysis/
		.
		.... agg-analysis/
		.
		.... Makefile

To compile all the code in the tools directory, change
to the tools directory and type "make all" from the
command line.

Refer to the README file in each of the subdirectories
for details about its contents.

